reviewText: He was my step dads uncle! Very amazing experience being able to gift him  with uncle totch dvds he was beyond grateful!
Only one of the DVDs would play on my TV DVD.  They did play on my iMac DVD.  Frustrating.
Nothing like the Ten  Thousand Islands and Loren G. TOTCH  Brown!  If you are a Florida Cracker , you will like this 6 dvd Set!
